            <h1 class="headline" style="font-size: 2.8rem;">Context & Background</h1>
            <p class="text-content">
                Tech reshapes theatre: not lost but adapting (Paksoy, 2025, p.8). Digital age, pandemic, and scrolling culture create new theatrical possibilities.
            </p>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item" data-popup="1960s: Morton Heilig's Sensorama - First immersive experience">
